title: Oleg Yelyshev
text:
Oleg Vyacheslavovich Yelyshev (; born 30 May 1971) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> player
Club career.
He played for several clubs in Europe and Asia, including <a href="FC%20Baltika%20Kaliningrad">Baltika Kaliningrad</a> and <a href="FC%20Fakel-Voronezh%20Voronezh">Fakel Voronezh</a> in the <a href="Soviet%20First%20League">Soviet First League</a>, <a href="FC%20Dynamo%20Moscow">Dynamo Moscow</a>, <a href="FC%20Tekstilshchik%20Kamyshin">Tekstilshchik Kamyshin</a> and <a href="FC%20Lokomotiv%20Moscow">Lokomotiv Moscow</a> in the <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> and <a href="FC%20Seoul">FC Seoul</a> of the <a href="South%20Korea">South Korea</a>n <a href="K-League">K-League</a>, then known as Anyang LG Cheetahs. and <a href="Hapoel%20Haifa%20F.C.">Hapoel Haifa</a> in the <a href="Israeli%20Premier%20League">Israeli Premier League</a>.
